00:27:46.830 --> 00:27:48.510
envolvido na contenda do tribunal.

00:27:49.680 --> 00:27:52.400
Para salvar a cidade,

00:27:52.830 --> 00:27:54.310
Eu decidi mudar

00:27:54.960 --> 00:27:57.510
